Subject: Re: [T2] Gas smell in rear bench seat belts inserts.

Hi Arnaud,

Sounds to me that one of the rubber couplings between the tank and  
the vent line have decayed.

They are part number 24 here:
http://www.ratwell.com/technical/Microfiche/t202110.gif

Deal with this ASAP and carry a fire extinguisher in the meanwhile.

